messages.message: Hey, anyone else’s sandbox still getting stuck on the CustomizeHome step? I’m not seeing any errors/retries like I normally would if it’s a kubeconfig issue.
Even my sandbox (https://instabase.sandboxes.site/sandboxes/prakhar-sb?cw=dev) is stuck at the same step. I forgot to suspend the sandbox and it has been going on for almost 3h now.

Based on these logs for Liam's sandbox (https://instabase.sandboxes.site/logviewx/instabase/liamcallanan/dev/task/setup%3ACustomizeHome) it appears to have completed successfully completed in a reasonable amount of time (17 seconds)?
Yeah I’m not sure what changed but it’s no longer hanging now. My sandbox works but I’m seeing “unknown” as the status for everything in the “Processes” table
looks like you haven't enabled any intercepted services at the moment :slightly_smiling_face:
